    • drawTest

      @Test public void drawTest()
      This method tests for draw method. When a crack is made, it's not null when it's to be drawn on screen.

    • resetTest

      @Test public void resetTest()
      This method tests for reset method. To test whether a crack has been reset, I assume everything is reset, so the cement brick is not broken and the strength of cement brick is reset to 2. There is no way to check the drawing, or at least I can't find it, so I did it this way.
